result.name: Fairwood

reviews.text: Usually find table. Only fast food cafe on this street. If music be softer will be better.
Decent portions and flavour. Good for a quick bite

The food is generally acceptable and the price is also fair. Their service is just horrible especially the folks at the food collecting area. More than once I have witness verbal jarring between them and customers, and the manager had to step in to stop the staff from causing more damage. Come if you want to save some money and have decent food, but don't expect anything spectacular. The overall hygiene of the establishment can also be improved.
Not recommended, at least for not for breakfast

result.name: 大快活

reviews.text: 好吃😋
應該是幫襯過的大快活最差的一間，除了早餐ok,午餐晚餐是很難吃，難怪一直門可羅雀，這次吃普通的粟米肉粒飯，配菜是已變色，有股奇怪餿味，肉粒偏少，可以的話，真的不要去。
1973年荃灣眾安街第一間
此處人流不多,除左住客都好小外人幫襯!
